017/03/DragonBall3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-972\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tulisan Garam Pedas (pulsk.com)</p></div>\n<p>Kalau kita lihat pada gambar-gambar diatas, terlihat bahwa banyak sekali tulisan-tulisan berbahasa Indonesia di sekitar lokasi kejuaraan.</p>\n<p><strong>Kemunculan Seseorang dengan Tulisan Budhiyasa di Lengan Bajunya</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_977\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-977\" data-attachment-id=\"977\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ternyata-banyak-unsur-indonesia-di-manga-dragon-ball-lho/attachment/dragonball4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tulisan Budhiyasa di Lengan Karakter\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tulisan Budhiyasa di Lengan Karakter  (malesbanget.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-977\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall4.jpg\" alt=\"Tulisan Budhiyasa di Lengan Karakter (malesbanget.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-977\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tulisan Budhiyasa di Lengan Karakter (malesbanget.com)</p></div>\n<p>Daaan&#8230; usut punya usut, ternyata Budhiyasa adalah</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_992\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-992\" data-attachment-id=\"992\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ternyata-banyak-unsur-indonesia-di-manga-dragon-ball-lho/attachment/dragonball7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall7.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Budhiyasa yang Asli\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Budhiyasa yang Asli (dragonball.wikia.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall7-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall7.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-992\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall7.jpg\" alt=\"Budhiyasa yang Asli (dragonball.wikia.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall7.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall7-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-992\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Budhiyasa yang Asli (dragonball.wikia.com)</p></div>\n<p>Dari sini aja kita bisa tau ya. Kalo sang penulis memang pernah liburan ke Bali dan dapet banyak inspirasi dari situ. Eits&#8230; tunggu dulu, masi ada satu bukti lagi nih.</p>\n<p><strong>Munculnya Nama-nama Tempat di Pulau Bali</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_987\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-987\" data-attachment-id=\"987\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ternyata-banyak-unsur-indonesia-di-manga-dragon-ball-lho/attachment/dragonball6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tulisan Bali\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tulisan Bali (duniaku.net)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-987\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall6.jpg\" alt=\"Tulisan Bali (duniaku.net)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-987\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tulisan Bali (duniaku.net)</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_982\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-982\" data-attachment-id=\"982\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ternyata-banyak-unsur-indonesia-di-manga-dragon-ball-lho/attachment/dragonball5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Tulisan Singaraja\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Tulisan Singaraja (duniaku.net)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-982\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall5.jpg\" alt=\"Tulisan Singaraja (duniaku.net)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/DragonBall5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-982\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tulisan Singaraja (duniaku.net)</p></div>\n<p>Gimana? Udah Fix banget nihh kalo Akira Toriyama memang terinspirasi sama keindahan pulau dewata kita yag tercinta. Tapi serem juga sih kalo Songoku dan kawan-kawan beneran ada dan bertarung di Bali. Karena di komiknya (Dragon Ball volume 16) ada adegan dimana Pikkoro ngancurin pulau! Coba bayangin tuhh, gimana jadinya kalo itu kejadian beneran!</p>\n<p>Bangga nggak sih? Sampe penulis komik legendaris selevel Akira Toriyama aja ngambil inspirasi dari Indonesia. Nah&#8230; Buat kamu-kamu yang juga lagi butuh inspirasi, gak usah jauh-jauh pergi keluar negri buat dapetin ide. Coba aja kamu liburan keliling-keliling Indonesia, dijamin bakalan banyak inspirasi yang bisa kamu dapetin dari situ.</p>\n<p>Selain Dragon Ball, pecinta komik manga ada yang tau nggak manga lainnya yang terinspirasi sama Indonesia? Share ke kita ya kalo ada! dan buat kalian yang suka baca komik, yuk kepoin Ciayo Comics yang punya segudang komik keren lainnya!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"e749f6ad-718a-5fa4-a7ad-c404421b2bd2"}}}